             re-examined. Q. To what period are you allading, when you say the prisoner confessed? A. In my parlour, on the 23rd, and at the Mansion-house on the 24th.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 25.</p>
